<Name>Cartesian coordinates</Name>
<Active>true</Active>
<Content>
<Comment><![CDATA[Cï¿½lculo de las posiciones en coordenadas cartesianas]]></Comment>
<Code><![CDATA[
if (leftSide) {
  x1 =   0;
  y1 = - d;
}
else {
  x1 =   d * Math.sin(theta);
  y1 = - d * Math.cos(theta);
}
x2 = x1 + (lTotal-d)*Math.sin(theta);
y2 = y1 - (lTotal-d)*Math.cos(theta);

]]></Code>

</Content>
